        <p>You and the computer draw cards till one of you is 21 or closer to it. The computer stops drawing after 17. Aces count as 1, and face cards as 10.</p>
        <a href="@Url.Action("BlackJackIndex", "Games", null)">
            <span class="btn btn-primary">Play Game</span>
        </a>
    </div>

