    <h2>High Low</h2>
    <p>2 cards are picked by the dealer one shown the other folded you have to guess whether the second card will be lower or higher. guess right and you win. not and you lose.</p>
    <a href="@Url.Action("HighLowIndex", "Games", null)">
        <span class="btn btn-primary">Play Game</span>
